Chipotle Aioli

5 min
$2.5
100 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

Description

A smoky, creamy sauce that adds a spicy kick to any dish.

Ingredients

  • mayonnaise: 1 cup
  • chipotle peppers in adobo sauce: 2-3 peppers
  • garlic: 1 clove
  • lime juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
